name: Trainer 1
Dialogue: You heading to FUCHSIA?

name: Trainer 1 after
Dialogue: I love racing downhill!

name: Trainer 2
Dialogue: What do you want, kiddo?

name: Trainer 2 after
Dialogue: I could belly-bump you outta here!

name: Trainer 3
Dialogue: There's no money in fighting kids!

name: Trainer 3 after
Dialogue: Good stuff is lying around on CYCLING ROAD!

name: Trainer 4
Dialogue: We're BIKERs! Highway stars!

name: Trainer 4 after
Dialogue: Are you looking for adventure?

name: Trainer 5
Dialogue: I need a little exercise!

name: Trainer 5 after
Dialogue: I'm sure I lost weight there!

name: Trainer 6
Dialogue: Nice BIKE! How's it handle?

name: Trainer 6 after
Dialogue: The slope makes it hard to steer!

name: Trainer 7
Dialogue: Let VOLTORB electrify you!

name: Trainer 7 after
Dialogue: I got my VOLTORB at the abandoned POWER PLANT.

name: Trainer 8
Dialogue: My POKEMON won't evolve! Why?

name: Trainer 8 after
Dialogue: Maybe some POKEMON need element STONEs to evolve.

name: Trainer 9
Dialogue: Be a rebel!

name: Trainer 9 after
Dialogue: Be ready to fight for your beliefs!

name: Trainer 10
Dialogue: Get lost kid! I'm bushed!

name: Trainer 10 after
Dialogue: I need to catch a few Zs!

name: Signpost 1
Dialogue: It's a notice! Watch out for discarded items!

name: Signpost 2
Dialogue:
TRAINER TIPS
All POKEMON are unique. Even POKEMON of the same type and level
grow at different rates.

name: Signpost 3
Dialogue:
TRAINER TIPS
Press the A or B Button to stay in place while on a slope.

name: Signpost 4
Dialogue: It's a notice! Don't throw the game, throw POKE BALLs instead!

name: Signpost 5
Dialogue:
CYCLING ROAD
Slope ends here!
